(1028, 1, '2017-09-24 01:04:58', '2017-09-24 01:04:58', 'The ASUS ROG Poseidon GeForce GTX 1080 Ti Platinum graphics card features a 1620MHz base clock with a 1733MHz boost clock, 11GB 352-bit GDDR5X memory, PCI-E 3.0, 11100MHz memory clock, Patented Wing-Blade IP5X-Certified Fans, ASUS Aura Sync, Standard G1/4-Inch Terminal Block, Next-Gen DirectCU H2O Hybrid Cooling, OpenGL 4.5 support, DirectX 12 support, DVI-D, 2x HDMI 2.0 and 2x DisplayPort. Backed by a 3 year ASUS warranty.', 'ASUS ROG Poseidon GeForce GTX 1080 Ti Platinum 11GB', 'The ASUS ROG Poseidon GeForce GTX 1080 Ti Platinum graphics card features a 1620MHz base clock with a 1733MHz boost clock,', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'asus-rog-poseidon-geforce-gtx-1080-ti-platinum-11gb', '', '', '2017-09-24 02:07:33', '2017-09-24 02:07:33', '', 0, 'https://nas.local/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=1028', 0, 'product', '', 0),
