(1042, 1, '2017-09-24 01:18:49', '2017-09-24 01:18:49', 'The LG 34UM68-P Ultrawide LED Gaming Monitor features a massive 34in IPS display with a 2560x1080 resolution, 5ms GTG response time, 75Hz refresh rate, sRGB over 99%, VESA 100mm support, speakers, Black Stabilizer, Game Mode, 2x HDMI, DisplayPort 1.2 and more. The UltraWide 21:9 aspect ratio makes games and movies more immersive than ever. The clarity of 1080p with IPS is a game-changer. Simply put, from any viewing angle, everything looks more crisp and detailed in full HD.', 'LG 34UM68-P 34in Ultrawide FreeSync IPS LED Gaming Monitor', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lg-34um68-p-34in-ultrawide-freesync-ips-led-gaming-monitor', '', '', '2017-09-24 02:27:15', '2017-09-24 02:27:15', '', 0, 'https://nas.local/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=1042', 0, 'product', '', 0),
