(1045, 2, '2017-09-24 01:23:09', '2017-09-24 01:23:09', '<strong>Overview</strong>\r\n\r\nTake document scanning to a whole new level with the ScanSnap S1300 mobile scanning solution. Whether you\'re at home digitising receipts, bank statements or term papers, or at the office capturing mission critical documents for a business trip, ScanSnap takes scanning beyond the desktop and into your world.\r\n\r\n<strong>Features and Specs</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>600 x 600 Scan DPI</li>\r\n 	<li>ADF (Automatic Document Feeder). Duplex color scanning</li>\r\n 	<li>Scanning Speed: 8 seconds per page</li>\r\n 	<li>Scan to iPad &amp; iPhone with apprpriate apps</li>\r\n 	<li>Holds up to 10 pages in the automatic document feeder</li>\r\n 	<li>Cross-platform compatibility for PC and Mac</li>\r\n 	<li>One button Searchable PDF creation, PDF, and JPEG</li>\r\n 	<li>Scan to editable Word and Excel files</li>\r\n 	<li>Create searchable keywords from highlighter text</li>\r\n 	<li>Business card scanning software</li>\r\n 	<li>USB or AC powered</li>\r\n 	<li>Intelligent Scan Correction</li>\r\n 	<li>USB Cable Included</li>\r\n 	<li>12 Months Warranty</li>\r\n 	<li>Dimensions (WxDXH): 400 x 200 x 150 mm</li>\r\n 	<li>Weight: 2.5kg</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Fujitsu ScanSnap S1300i Instant', 'Take document scanning to a whole new level with the ScanSnap S1300 mobile scanning solution. Whether you\'re at home digitising receipts, bank statements or term papers, or at the office capturing mission critical documents for a business trip, ScanSnap takes scanning beyond the desktop and into your world.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'fujitsu-scansnap-s1300i-instant', '', '', '2017-09-24 04:18:07', '2017-09-24 04:18:07', '', 0, 'https://nas.local/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=1045', 0, 'product', '', 0),
