(1050, 2, '2017-09-24 01:33:24', '2017-09-24 01:33:24', 'The ASUS DSL-AC52U is a ADSL/VDSL 802.11ac Wi-Fi modem router, with combined dual-band data rates of up to 733Mbps. On the 5GHz band, 802.11ac gives 433Mbps wireless data rates, while 2.4 GHz 802.11n performance supports 300Mbps. Compatible with ADSL2/2+, ADSL, VDSL2, fiber and cable services, the DSL-AC52U is future-proof.\r\n\r\n<b>Features:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Concurrent Dual Band: 433Mbps on 5GHz and 300Mbps on 2.4GHz</li>\r\n 	<li>Two WAN ports for DSL and Ethernet offer double the choice  wireless router or DSL modem</li>\r\n 	<li>Compatible with VDSL2, ADSL2/2+, ADSL, fiber and cable services for complete future-proofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Gigabit Ethernet ports for the fastest, most reliable internet performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Multi-purpose USB port supports file sharing, printer sharing, media streaming and 3G/4G support</li>\r\n 	<li>VDSL/ADSL WAN multi service for IPTV support</li>\r\n 	<li>PPTP/Open VPN server and VPN client support</li>\r\n 	<li>Download Master and enhanced media server let you download and stream anywhere</li>\r\n 	<li>ASUS AiCloud lets you access, sync, share and stream data anywhere</li>\r\n</ul>', 'ASUS DSL-AC52U Dual Band Wireless ADSL/VDSL Modem Router', 'The ASUS DSL-AC52U is a ADSL/VDSL 802.11ac Wi-Fi modem router, with combined dual-band data rates of up to 733Mbps. On the 5GHz band, 802.11ac gives 433Mbps wireless data rates, while 2.4 GHz 802.11n performance supports 300Mbps. Compatible with ADSL2/2+, ADSL, VDSL2, fiber and cable services, the DSL-AC52U is future-proof.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'asus-dsl-ac52u-dual-band-wireless-adslvdsl-modem-router', '', '', '2017-09-24 02:18:25', '2017-09-24 02:18:25', '', 0, 'https://nas.local/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=1050', 0, 'product', '', 0),
